{"tid":1099422,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"12月尾西藏跨年好凍之旅","createTime":"2019-04-09T19:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T14:55:12.000Z","uid":109631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d605dc5ccb197882be98c6792b102a94ae80f2f","tid":1099422,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T19:02:19.000Z","msg":"第一次寫少少分享，遊記就唔長寫啦，西藏好多人都有寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋我鐘意直接睇景成日唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前期篇<br />\n1/點入藏<br />\n我係香港飛西安，係西安玩下再飛拉薩<br />\n至於點解係西安，只係想睇下古蹟<br />\n可以飛拉薩嘅地方仲有好多，一陣再講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpjjPUM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpjjPUM.png&h=bc33945e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtFK01S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtFK01S.png&h=aa5cfc09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個晚餐都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢個本身唔係晚餐，因為有軍事活動班機delay咗好多，所以咩景都無得睇，到拉薩已經10點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落機時-10度左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oz1Vog1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foz1Vog1.png&h=3ccf10c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過西藏咁靚幾凍都值得啦係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2/機票<br />\n去西藏主要都係火車飛機拼車，我飛機入火車出，飛機票可以用12306/<a href=\"http://trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrip.com&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=c3f9aa94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">trip.com</a>等等買，今次我就用大陸app 飛豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終12306個verify過程係有啲煩，唔係人人都可以做到<br />\n<br />\n西藏嘅機票只要你淡季去，其實都可以好平，西寧以外，西安/重慶/鄭州等等都有得出發，單程200-900人民幣不等，今次200左右搭西藏航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話有飛機餐食我當賺咗㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOvSqT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOvSqT2.png&h=9c14dcb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3/高反<br />\n天氣寒冷加飛機入藏，大啲機會有高反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以今次飛前一日就食咗高反藥，都係大家食開嘅acetazolamide，唔係diamox brand 啫<br />\n去到無咩高反，只係好攰（可能係高反嘅一種）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjKWSny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjKWSny.png&h=89da9cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時講住咁多先，有機會再講<br />\nBtw 拉薩四川化問題好嚴重，仲想去到感受下西藏風情好快啲去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b021c5261087bd230990da1a78e8755bca0ef59d","tid":1099422,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T19:51:03.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ee4e0168f89642b7abf1dd6dfe2184c031409d","tid":1099422,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T23:06:06.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276e4d7b932174b1aa9738f338d583015f449795","tid":1099422,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8229f6d9faa80ae4ad8d9f6fd96be768637801f3","tid":1099422,"uid":192494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}